::Fenox::

Fenox looks toward D in surprise as the wolf-bot growls, looking even 
more surprised when she sees that his head was almost right next to 
hers. She strokes his fur reassuringly with one hand and then looks 
back at Vlad.

"You'll have to exuse him, he's new here," she says, smiling at Vlad.
